elements.name: updateStatus
elements.description: A code representing the status of the update. Valid Update Status Codes are: U = Update Acknowledgment. Record Identifier $6 is system generated if an error-free condition exists. E = Error Condition. Record Identifier $7 is system generated if an error condition exists.

elements.name: updateSequenceNumber
elements.description: The International Organization for Standardization (ISO) country code representing the location of the firm for all countries except Canada. Valid ISO codes are listed in Appendix B of this publication.
